CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS DataCo.order_items (
    order_item_id int NOT NULL,
    order_item_order_id int,
    order_item_product_id int,
    order_item_quantity tinyint,
    order_item_subtotal float,
    order_item_product_price float
);

2.1.3 DataCo Delta Lake script
CREATE DATABASE IF NOT EXISTS DataCo;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS DataCo.categories (
    category_id int NOT NULL,
    category_department_id int,
    category_name varchar(45)
);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS DataCo.customers (
    customer_id int NOT NULL,
    customer_fname varchar(45),
    customer_lname varchar(45),
    -- customer_email varchar(45), customer_password varchar(45), customer_address struct<customer_street: varchar(45), customer_city: varchar(45), customer_state: varchar(45), customer_zipcode: varchar(45)>, `new_property` string
);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS DataCo.departments (
    department_id int NOT NULL,
    department_name varchar(255)
);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS DataCo.order_items (
    order_item_id int NOT NULL,
    order_item_order_id int,
    order_item_product_id int,
    order_item_quantity tinyint,
    order_item_subtotal float,
    order_item_product_price float
);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS DataCo.orders (
    order_id int NOT NULL,
    order_date date,
    order_customer_id int,
    order_status varchar(45)
) COMMENT 'Table holding customer orders';
USE DataCo;
ALTER TABLE
    orders
ADD
    CONSTRAINT `order_date_constraint` CHECK (order_date > '1900-01-01');

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS DataCo.products (
    product_id int NOT NULL,
    product_category_id int,
    product_name char(45),
    product_description varchar(255),
    product_price float,
    product_image varchar(255)
);

CREATE VIEW IF NOT EXISTS DataCo.orders_view AS
SELECT
    DataCo.orders.order_id as order_id,
    DataCo.orders.order_date as order_date,
    DataCo.orders.order_status as order_status,
    DataCo.orders.order_customer_id as order_customer_id,
    DataCo.customers.customer_fname as customer_fname,
    DataCo.customers.customer_lname as customer_lname,
    DataCo.customers.customer_address as customer_address,
    DataCo.order_items.order_item_id as order_item_id,
    DataCo.order_items.order_item_product_id as order_item_product_id,
    DataCo.products.product_name as product_name,
    DataCo.order_items.order_item_quantity as order_item_quantity,
    DataCo.order_items.order_item_subtotal as order_item_subtotal,
    DataCo.order_items.order_item_product_price as order_item_product_price
FROM
    DataCo.orders
    INNER JOIN DataCo.customers
    INNER JOIN DataCo.order_items
    INNER JOIN DataCo.products;
